high_descs: Look down at the sink in front of you.
Pick up the spoon that is in the sink.
Turn around so that the dishwasher is in front of you, to your left side.
Place the spoon on the counter space above the dishwasher, to the left of the tomato.
Walk forward, hanging a right once you reach the stove, then walk a few steps, and turn right again to face the green table.
Pick up the spoon that is between the head of lettuce and the metal spatula on the table.
Turn to your right, hang a left when the stove is on your right, then walk to the kitchen sink and face the stove area.
Place the spoon behind the tomato that sits on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two spoons to the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Move forward to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from inside the sink next to the bottle.
Turn right and to the right of the sink.
Put the spoon on the counter on the right side of the sink.
Approach the stove and turn right to the head of the table.
Pick up the spoon closest to you, slightly under the spatula handle.
Turn right and go to the right side of the sink.
Put the spoon on the counter behind the apple.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the spoons from the sink and table, put them both on the counter.

high_descs: Look down at the cabinets under the counter and walk to the sink ahead.
Pick up the spoon from inside the sink in the middle.
Turn around, turn left at the green table and face towards the white stove ahead.
Put the spoon on the counter to the left side in front of the tomato.
Cross the room, hang a right at the stove and turn right just beyond the stove to face the green table.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the spatula on the table.
Turn right, hang a left at the stove, turn right just before the black fridge and face right towards the stove ahead.
Put the spoon on the green counter to the left in between the other spoon and the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place two spoons on a counter.
